574
00:34:56,560 --> 00:34:57,280
Don't be annoyed anymore.

575
00:34:58,120 --> 00:34:59,240
I'll tell you a piece of good news.

576
00:35:00,400 --> 00:35:01,440
Ling Ling is back?

577
00:35:03,640 --> 00:35:04,720
She hasn't entered the city yet.

578
00:35:38,440 --> 00:35:38,880
Come.

579
00:35:46,360 --> 00:35:47,280
Why are you here?

580
00:35:47,720 --> 00:35:49,400
I feel like I haven't seen you
for a long time.

581
00:35:50,160 --> 00:35:51,360
I especially came to congratulate you

582
00:35:51,480 --> 00:35:52,360
after hearing of your victorious return.

583
00:35:52,680 --> 00:35:53,880
You don't need to do this, Master.

584
00:35:54,000 --> 00:35:55,280
I'll do it myself.

585
00:35:57,120 --> 00:35:57,960
Master?

586
00:35:58,800 --> 00:36:00,040
Since I'm your confidant,

587
00:36:00,160 --> 00:36:01,480
of course I must call you Master.

588
00:36:02,600 --> 00:36:03,760
I don't see

589
00:36:03,760 --> 00:36:05,200
your willingness to do so.

590
00:36:06,360 --> 00:36:07,120
You know what?

591
00:36:07,280 --> 00:36:09,200
Sincerity must be exchanged
with sincerity.

592
00:36:09,320 --> 00:36:10,440
What you're doing to me

593
00:36:10,440 --> 00:36:11,120
is coercion and bribery.

594
00:36:11,200 --> 00:36:12,800
Of course there won't be any willingness
on my part.

595
00:36:13,960 --> 00:36:14,760
Someday,

596
00:36:14,840 --> 00:36:16,160
you'll become willing.

597
00:36:17,640 --> 00:36:18,440
How's your injury?

598
00:36:18,560 --> 00:36:19,240
Let me check.

599
00:36:20,840 --> 00:36:21,680
I'm not injured.

600
00:36:21,800 --> 00:36:23,000
Who told you that I'm injured?

601
00:36:24,280 --> 00:36:24,720
By the way,

602
00:36:25,000 --> 00:36:26,080
I have something to tell you.

603
00:36:26,320 --> 00:36:27,600
In the list of people

604
00:36:27,600 --> 00:36:28,640
entering the palace tomorrow,

605
00:36:28,760 --> 00:36:29,720
my name is included.

606
00:36:31,800 --> 00:36:32,920
Ling Ling is included,

607
00:36:33,440 --> 00:36:34,440
not Cheng Ruoyu.

608
00:36:35,200 --> 00:36:35,920
Have you forgotten?

609
00:36:36,240 --> 00:36:37,600
Cheng Ruoyu is already dead.

610
00:36:45,360 --> 00:36:46,360
Qi Yan is alive.

611
00:36:46,640 --> 00:36:47,440
He's doing well.

612
00:36:47,960 --> 00:36:48,800
Isn't that enough?

613
00:36:49,200 --> 00:36:49,760
No.

614
00:36:49,880 --> 00:36:51,440
I want to personally see him
before I can feel at ease.

615
00:36:52,280 --> 00:36:52,800
Yanzhi.

616
00:36:53,160 --> 00:36:54,600
I'm back in the capital now.

617
00:36:54,800 --> 00:36:56,400
I'll surely see His Majesty.

618
00:36:56,560 --> 00:36:57,880
You can stop me once or twice.

619
00:36:58,000 --> 00:36:59,280
But can you stop me forever?

620
00:37:07,160 --> 00:37:07,880
Fine.

621
00:37:09,600 --> 00:37:11,200
It's good for you to have closure
with him as well.

622
00:37:15,680 --> 00:37:17,240
After seeing Qi Yan tomorrow,

623
00:37:17,400 --> 00:37:18,840
return to Chess of Generals Camp.

624
00:37:20,120 --> 00:37:20,840
I'll wait for you.

625
00:37:22,760 --> 00:37:24,080
I have a question for you.

626
00:37:24,240 --> 00:37:25,840
Why did you name me Ling Ling?

627
00:37:25,920 --> 00:37:26,600
Does this name

628
00:37:26,600 --> 00:37:28,040
have a special meaning?

629
00:37:32,360 --> 00:37:34,920
It's hard to comment on the corruption
and decline of people.

630
00:37:36,200 --> 00:37:38,120
There's a huge difference
between their reputations.

631
00:37:39,240 --> 00:37:41,280
The honest are abandoned,

632
00:37:42,360 --> 00:37:44,000
and corrupt ones
are increasingly favored.

633
00:37:47,240 --> 00:37:50,720
I hope you'll always remember that.

634
00:37:51,480 --> 00:37:54,040
The honest are...

635
00:37:55,160 --> 00:37:56,360
I don't understand.

636
00:37:58,280 --> 00:37:59,360
What does that mean?

637
00:38:18,240 --> 00:38:19,280
The army is victorioius.

638
00:38:19,680 --> 00:38:21,480
Why are you unhappy, Your Majesty?

639
00:38:24,720 --> 00:38:26,440
Someone wants to provoke me.

640
00:38:28,920 --> 00:38:30,160
How can I feel happy?

641
00:38:35,360 --> 00:38:36,000
Huaizhi.

642
00:38:36,920 --> 00:38:37,560
Yes.

643
00:38:38,360 --> 00:38:39,800
If someone tells you

644
00:38:41,240 --> 00:38:42,440
that Yu'er is alive,

645
00:38:48,160 --> 00:38:48,880
will you believe it?

646
00:38:52,440 --> 00:38:53,520
For real, Your Majesty?

647
00:38:53,880 --> 00:38:55,120
Yu'er is alive?

648
00:38:55,480 --> 00:38:56,120
Yu'er.

649
00:38:57,320 --> 00:38:58,120
This is great.

650
00:38:58,360 --> 00:38:59,080
Your Majesty.

651
00:38:59,280 --> 00:39:00,880
Where is Yu'er now?

652
00:39:06,440 --> 00:39:07,160
Look.

653
00:39:10,000 --> 00:39:11,320
You're very happy indeed.

654
00:39:14,440 --> 00:39:15,920
Even if there's only a gleam of hope,

655
00:39:17,200 --> 00:39:19,000
you're willing to believe
that she's still alive.

656
00:39:22,600 --> 00:39:23,320
Your Majesty.

657
00:39:24,560 --> 00:39:25,800
I'm slow.

658
00:39:27,160 --> 00:39:28,560
I don't know what you mean.

659
00:39:37,360 --> 00:39:38,320
Chess of Generals Camp

660
00:39:39,440 --> 00:39:39,960
found a woman

661
00:39:39,960 --> 00:39:41,280
who looks like Yu'er.

662
00:39:43,080 --> 00:39:44,640
They'll let her say
that she's Cheng Ruoyu

663
00:39:45,280 --> 00:39:46,600
and return to my side.

664
00:39:48,880 --> 00:39:49,560
Your Majesty.

665
00:39:50,440 --> 00:39:52,840
What is their objective in doing so?

666
00:39:54,000 --> 00:39:55,000
Since Qiu Ziliang

667
00:39:57,120 --> 00:39:59,240
doesn't want me to continue living,

668
00:40:00,000 --> 00:40:04,000
