to ascend to the throne?

669
00:40:05,760 --> 00:40:06,600
That's why

670
00:40:08,160 --> 00:40:09,000
he's waiting.

671
00:40:12,000 --> 00:40:13,600
He's waiting for me to have a son.

672
00:40:15,240 --> 00:40:16,400
Your Majesty, all these years,

673
00:40:17,000 --> 00:40:18,480
the only woman you've been close with

674
00:40:18,640 --> 00:40:19,600
is Yu'er.

675
00:40:20,920 --> 00:40:22,160
Then they want...

676
00:40:23,840 --> 00:40:24,720
They want

677
00:40:26,640 --> 00:40:28,120
to create a fake Yu'er

678
00:40:29,440 --> 00:40:31,160
to give birth to a royal son.

679
00:40:54,320 --> 00:40:55,720
I can finally see His Majesty.

