696
00:43:06,440 --> 00:43:07,560
"In the Chancellery,

697
00:43:07,920 --> 00:43:10,560
Acting Military Commissioner
Zhang Zhongru

698
00:43:11,120 --> 00:43:13,560
led 800 elite warriors

699
00:43:14,080 --> 00:43:15,720
