708
00:43:35,840 --> 00:43:38,600
He's given the title of Prince Lanling.

709
00:43:39,120 --> 00:43:40,280
The rest of the troops

710
00:43:40,360 --> 00:43:42,000
will be awarded accordingly.

711
00:43:42,120 --> 00:43:46,000
In addition, everyone will be given
ten decaliter of grains

712
00:43:46,480 --> 00:43:48,520
and ten pieces of cloth.

713
00:43:48,960 --> 00:43:50,880
That's the imperial command."

714
00:43:51,600 --> 00:43:53,800
- Thank you, Your Majesty.
- Thank you, Your Majesty.

