718
00:44:03,080 --> 00:44:05,800
I'm a bit tired today.

719
00:44:06,800 --> 00:44:07,640
You're dismissed.

720
00:44:09,880 --> 00:44:11,960
Take care, Your Majesty.

721
00:44:14,280 --> 00:44:16,360
